Invocation Name: chemistry cheat sheet
des: This allows Alexa to read out Chemistry notes on IGCSE chemistry topic wise to students. It contains the key concepts which the student needs to come out with flying colors. This help as students feel that they are being taught one more time. This, being better for the student as it is more effective than reading the textbook, is a more advantageous way.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
